data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! The wait is over! Here's your dream home!!  Open design floor plan.  This home has it all.  This amazing 2 story, 4-bedroom home is located on a large corner lot. Inside awaits custom features throughout. Updated light fixtures for romantic mood ambiance.  Downstairs offers one bedroom and bath, cozy living room and open kitchen with island.  Upstairs one oversize loft, master bedroom featuring a walk-in shower, walk-in closet and balcony.  This home boasts a seamless blend of elegance and functionality.  Jack & Jill baths with ample space and walk-in closets. The list is endless!
